query.esql:
from logs-corelight.dns*
| limit 10000
| where event.dataset == "dns" and observer.hostname is not null and (source.ip not in ("0.0.0.0","255.255.255.255") or destination.ip not in ("0.0.0.0","255.255.255.255")) and dns.question.type is not null and dns.question.type != "PTR"
| stats COUNT() by source.ip, dns.response_code, destination.domain, dns.question.type 
| stats COUNT() by destination.domain  
| rename destination.domain as Query,`COUNT()` as Count
| sort Count desc
| limit 10
| keep Query, Count
